::Firaxis::
       He turns to face her again.  He smiles slightly and bows formally.  
"By your leave, madam."  He executes a sharp salute and turns on his heel.  
He marches briskly back to his ship.  He opens a com to SFC "I'll be at the 
base shortly, I expect you to have the blank protoform ready upon my 
arrival."  He takes off and heads toward the base.

--part1_173.6aa3ac1.29eb7411_boundary
